title: Club bug of RM$
body:
Hi , im the owner of the club RM$ but i cant see my club or anything? 
summoner name is PESU5

replies.body: A while ago a[ club outage ](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/nMisJPK8-clubs-outage-oct-2016)cause this issue for some club owners, but it should be resolved.  If you still have this issue, hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can investigate your case individually to see what the deal is.  We'll get back to you!
